  <name>AB Download Manager</name>
  <summary>A Download Manager that speeds up your downloads</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      AB Download Manager is a desktop application that helps you manage and organize your downloads more efficiently than ever before.
    </p>
    <p>Key Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>⚡️ Faster Download Speed</li>
      <li>⏰ Queues and Schedulers</li>
      <li>🌐 Browser Extensions</li>
      <li>💻 Multiplatform (Windows / Linux / Mac)</li>
      <li>🌙 Multiple Themes (Dark/Light) with modern UI</li>
      <li>❤️ Free and Open Source</li>
      <li>⏸️ Pause, resume, and retry downloads</li>
      <li>📊 Download progress and statistics</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

